blocks.saveContent: Check out our Networking Mixer event, co-hosted by FLS Group and Promech Heavy Equipment, last month at the prestigious Pacific City Club Bangkok, Thailand.

blocks.saveContent: During the cosy event, we fostered great conversations with industry partners and clients while enjoying fantastic food, famous beers and wines as well as long drinks.
